Invoice
invoice_id        INT (Primary Key, Auto Increment)	Unique identifier
invoice_number    VARCHAR(50)	Invoice number (e.g., "INV-001")
invoice_date	DATE	Date invoice was created
created_at	TIMESTAMP	When record was created
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	When record was updated
category  VARCHAR(100)  Category of the invoice (e.g., "Travel", "Entertainment", "Office Supplies")
merchant_name  VARCHAR(255)  Name of the merchant
merchant_address  VARCHAR(255)  Address of the merchant
items_services  JSON  A JSON array to store details of items/services (name, quantity, price)
remark  TEXT  Any additional notes or remarks

Claim
id	INT (Primary Key, Auto Increment)	Unique identifier
claim_number	VARCHAR(50)	Human-readable claim number
invoice_id	INT (Foreign Key)	Reference to invoice table
employee_id	INT (Foreign Key)	Employee who submitted claim
claim_type	VARCHAR(50)	Type of claim
claim_amount	DECIMAL(10,2)	Amount being claimed
reason	TEXT	Detailed reason for the claim
status	VARCHAR(20)	Status (pending, approved, rejected)
submitted_date	DATE	When claim was submitted
reviewed_date	DATE	When claim was reviewed
resolution	TEXT	How the claim was resolved
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record creation timestamp
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	Last modification timestamp

Employee
id	INT (Primary Key, Auto Increment)	Unique identifier
employee_id	VARCHAR(20)	Company employee ID (e.g., "EMP001")
name	VARCHAR(50)	Employee name
email	VARCHAR(100)	Employee email address
password_hash	VARCHAR(255)	Encrypted password
phone	VARCHAR(20)	Phone number
department	VARCHAR(50)	Department name
job_title	VARCHAR(50)	Job title/position
hire_date	DATE	Date of hiring
salary	DECIMAL(10,2)	Employee salary
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record creation timestamp
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	Last modification timestamp

Admin
id	INT (Primary Key, Auto Increment)	Unique identifier
admin_id	VARCHAR(20)	Admin identifier (e.g., "ADM001")
username	VARCHAR(50)	Login username
password_hash	VARCHAR(255)	Encrypted password
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record creation timestamp
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	Last modification timestamp

Claim Policy
id	INT (Primary Key, Auto Increment)	Unique identifier
policy_name	VARCHAR(100)	Name of the policy (e.g., "Standard Refund Policy")
id_vector_db INT link to the MongoDB Policy
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record creation timestamp
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	Last modification timestamp
